===Overview===
The '''Rolling Stones''' are an English rock band formed in [[London (England)|London]], [[England]] in 1962. The first stable line-up consisted of [[Michael Jagger (Earth-616)|Mick Jagger]] as lead vocals, [[Keith Richards (Earth-616)|Keith Richards]] on guitar, [[Bill Wyman (Earth-616)|Bill Wyman]] on bass, and [[Charlie Watts (Earth-616)|Charlie Watts]] on the drums. 

===Events===
Keith's consciousness was transferred into an [[Life-Model Decoy]] ever "since ''[[wikipedia:Tattoo You|Tattoo You]]''," the Stones album released in 1981.{{r|Deadpool Vol 5 24}}
